{"tid":2050364,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【有片】TWICE SANA成為第一個跳「摸X舞」的女愛豆！動作100%還原全場笑翻","createTime":"2020-06-04T05:35:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-04T13:03:15.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"70602dafa46cd786c2c9f99839d906b25a600cc3","tid":2050364,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T05:35:47.000Z","msg":"Rain 3年前的歌曲《Gang》因為劉在錫而逆襲爆火，成為大家爭相模仿的對象，就連仙女團TWICE成員SANA也沒能逃過這首神曲的魅力。<br />\n<br />\n日前，TWICE做客了廣播節目《Power Time》，和聽眾們暢聊。 期間有聽眾表示想要看MOMO跳Rain的《Gang》，MOMO表示：「我自己沒有好好跳過，倒是和SANA一起跳過。 」DJ崔華靜立刻鼓勵兩人現場挑挑看。 MOMO和SANA稍微練習了之後就在演播廳的空地上跳了起來。 兩人將演播廳當做舞台，迎合著《Gang》的音樂起舞，在隊友們的「慫恿」下甚至展示了《Gang》的精髓動作「摸X舞」（摸辣椒舞，韓語中「辣椒」為男性生殖器的隱喻），逗得全場哈哈大笑。<br />\n<br />\n節目公開后不少網民留言稱：「SANA創造了歷史」、「哈哈哈哈，SANA太會了」、「第一個跳摸X舞的女愛豆」。 （大家可以從19:49開始看）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MA6w7S82Zzo&amp;feature=emb_title\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DMA6w7S82Zzo%26feature%3Demb_title&d=Fi4Me5dMHeyo7M%2BwlVraY6bKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=bb0a9f15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MA6w7S82Zzo&amp;feature=emb_title</a>"},{"pid":"63ee7297d28eb024c52a541a34be16b833184efb","tid":2050364,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T05:36:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsimgs.sina.tw/article/images/news-15912465026454.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsimgs.sina.tw%2Farticle%2Fimages%2Fnews-15912465026454.png&h=00a8d952&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://newsimgs.sina.tw/article/images/news-1591246506067.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsimgs.sina.tw%2Farticle%2Fimages%2Fnews-1591246506067.png&h=12c30483&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://newsimgs.sina.tw/article/images/news-15912465087337.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsimgs.sina.tw%2Farticle%2Fimages%2Fnews-1